  transition: opacity 300ms;
}

.modal-exit {
  opacity: 1;
}

.modal-exit-active {
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 300ms;
}
```

This will fade the modal in over 300ms when it's opened, and fade it out over 300ms when it's closed. The `unmountOnExit` prop means the modal will be unmounted from the DOM after the exit animation is complete.

